description:
&lt;p&gt;The Trust is seeking to appoint a highly motivated, enthusiastic and knowledgeable individual to the role of Systems Accountant within the Financial Directorate. The role will provide the necessary support to the Finance Directorate covering the below key tasks:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Finance Systems Administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reporting, including report automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Control and reconciliation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complex data analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate must possess good organisational, time management and communication skills, as well as heaving an exceptional technical knowledge in the use of systems within Finance and Excel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the job description and person specification to ensure that you have the necessary skills and experience to apply for the post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameLuke ArmstrongEmail addressLuke.Armstrong@nhs.netTelephone number01642854561&lt;/p&gt;
